save() - Method in class vveird.TabletopSoundboard.ngui.plugins.JPluginConfigurationPanel
Method is called by the gui if the save button of the Options Panel is pressed.
Changes should only be written down, if this method is called.
The activation/deactivation of the plugin should be done last.
